data.description: Welcome to this gorgeous Craftsman-Style home in Mundy Mill Subdivision. This beautiful two-story 5 bedroom, 3 full bath home has 2,344 sq ft of space to enjoy with family and friends. It also includes a 2 car garage. Home features an open concept kitchen with granite counter tops, tiled backsplash, and a walk-in pantry. Living room includes a fireplace to enjoy with family during the holidays. It has one bedroom and with full bath on main level perfect for guests. Includes a mud room with easy access from the garage. Upstairs you will find 4 spacious bedrooms with 2 full baths including the laundry room. The main bedroom features amazing double tray ceiling, crown molding, an enormous walk-in closet and much more features in main bathroom! The perfect place to raise a family only minutes away from schools and shopping. Luxury style amenities include lighted tennis courts, clubhouse, out door fireplace, gazebo, cabana, park with playground, and over-sized swimming pools with wading ends! This near new home built in 2016 is minutes from I-985 and Lake Lanier. A must see!!
